OL,5,     GJoin Dan Walker and the team for
OL,6,     Gthe news that matters to you.
OL,7,G1800FSusan Calman's Summer by the Sea
OL,8,     GIn Bournemouth, Susan takes a
OL,9,     Gbeachside train ride, boards a
OL,10,     Gferry to see impressive beach
OL,11,     Ghuts, visits a Victorian treasure
OL,12,     Gtrove and meets Gareth Malone for
OL,13,     Ga game of Jenga.
OL,14,G1900FDorset: Country and Coast
OL,15,     GWith miniature steam engines in
OL,16,     GPoole Quay, a visit to one of
OL,17,     GBournemouth's last family-run
OL,18,     Ghotels, and the ancient chalk
OL,19,     Ggiant cut into the hillside at
OL,20,     GCerne Abbas.
